---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Nat Emodi">
  <h1 class="name">Nat Emodi</h1>

  <p>
    I'm a founder building new companies at the frontier of consumer behavior and emerging technology: currently <a href="https://www.vie.game" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Vie.game</a>, and before that, <a href="https://www.highlight.xyz" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Highlight</a>. Previously, I worked at Square (now Block) and DoorDash.
  </p>

  <p>
    My work centers on turning early ideas into enduring businesses—across product strategy, design, and go-to-market. I've spent most of my career building teams and shipping products where the playbook doesn't yet exist.
  </p>

  <p>
    I spend my spare time chasing my kids around, enjoying nature, and cooking. I also invest in and advise early-stage startups.
  </p>

  <p>
    I grew up in Canada and studied at McGill University.
  </p>

  <p>
    You can find me on <a href="https://x.com/nemodi" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">𝕏</a>.
  </p>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .name {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  }
</style>
